	<h1 class="title">要培养好品味，不妨来看看这几本日本男性杂志</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">胡晓琪</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-02-27 08:00:16 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/22885/medium/22885.jpg?1456417039" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="22885" data-title="《要培养好品味，不妨来看看这几本日本男性杂志》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/22885/medium/22885.jpg?1456417039" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/22885.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
		<!-- 新浪微博 -->
